    "By incorporating cross-convolution blocks within the normalizing flow to assign probabilities, CS-Flow [53] makes use of the context within and between multi-scale feature maps to improve DifferNet.",
    "CFlow-AD [54] adds positional encoding to the framework for conditional normalizing flow to achieve superior results."
